    <div style={{fontSize:12,color:C.textMuted,textAlign:"center",lineHeight:1.5,margin:"14px 4px 0"}}>By continuing you agree to ClimbMatch's <span onClick={()=>onLegal&&onLegal("terms")} style={{color:C.blue,cursor:"pointer",textDecoration:"underline"}}>Terms</span> and acknowledge the <span onClick={()=>onLegal&&onLegal("privacy")} style={{color:C.blue,cursor:"pointer",textDecoration:"underline"}}>Privacy Policy</span>. Belay verification and guide vetting rely on accurate info.</div>
